testsuite.name: Test cases for pipeline dependencyMode and chronological

testcase.name: WORKFLOW_TESTS - pipeline workFlow tests Test cases for pipeline dependencyMode and chronological P_WF_0023. If waitOnParentComplete is in the child and waitOnChildComplete in the parent, the parent runs first.
testcase.classname: P_WF_0023. If waitOnParentComplete is in the child and waitOnChildComplete in the parent, the parent runs first.

testcase.name: WORKFLOW_TESTS - pipeline workFlow tests Test cases for pipeline dependencyMode and chronological P_WF_0024. If waitOnParentComplete is false and waitOnParentSuccess is true, the pipeline will only run when the last run was successful.
testcase.classname: P_WF_0024. If waitOnParentComplete is false and waitOnParentSuccess is true, the pipeline will only run when the last run was successful.

testcase.name: WORKFLOW_TESTS - pipeline workFlow tests Test cases for pipeline dependencyMode and chronological P_WF_0025. A user adds a child pipeline with waitOnParentComplete true and the parent updates a resource used by a step that is not the first in the pipeline, the child pipeline runs with the updated resource.
testcase.classname: P_WF_0025. A user adds a child pipeline with waitOnParentComplete true and the parent updates a resource used by a step that is not the first in the pipeline, the child pipeline runs with the updated resource.

testcase.name: WORKFLOW_TESTS - pipeline workFlow tests Test cases for pipeline dependencyMode and chronological P_WF_0026. If waitOnParentSuccess is true in the pipelines configuration section, the pipeline will run even if its parent has never run.
